%section
  %h2 What is the JBoss Way?
  %blockquote
    :markdown
      The JBoss Way shows you how to write applications using JBoss technologies.

      * Learn how to write an application suitable for mobile 
      * Learn how to use the Java EE 6 API with JBoss AS
      * Learn how to add the power of CDI to your browser

%section
  :markdown
    ## Highlights

    * 83 Quickstarts, focused on a single use case or API
    * Medium complexity example - TicketMonster, with Apache Cordova, and JBoss Data Grid
    * Stacks defined for Java EE, Errai, Hibernate, Arquillian, Transactions, DeltaSpike, RichFaces, Infinispan (more to come)
    * Migration guides for Spring, Seam 2 and Java EE 5
    * Archetypes - Java EE, RichFaces, Errai, HTML5

